\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Three-tier \texttt  {EvoClaw}\xspace  {} architecture with inter-component connections. Edge agents (Rust) execute skills and manage local memory. Server orchestrator (Go) coordinates agents via MQTT and routes LLM requests. Cloud services provide persistent storage (Turso), ephemeral compute (E2B), and blockchain identity (ClawChain). Solid arrows show control flow; dashed arrows show data flow.}}{4}{figure.caption.1}\protected@file@percent }
